Q: how to make less do color?
A: less -R

Q: how to make it simply exit if just one screen?
A: less -F

Q: how to make less and man not clear screen before and after?
A: less -X

Q: how to make less and man do all of the above, in bash?
A:
    alias less="less -X -F -R"
    export PAGER="less -X -F -R"

